259
00:14:28,656 --> 00:14:29,796
Here, thank you.

260
00:14:29,796 --> 00:14:30,926
- Keep up the good work. - Bye.

261
00:14:33,367 --> 00:14:35,666
- I'm back. - Do you want dinner?

262
00:14:36,166 --> 00:14:38,506
- I'm good. - Something's up, right?

263
00:14:39,406 --> 00:14:40,437
Tell me.

264
00:14:42,837 --> 00:14:45,577
Well, we have a new manager.

265
00:14:45,807 --> 00:14:48,217
He's blowing up the Audit Team.

266
00:14:49,847 --> 00:14:52,687
He declares he's right and everyone is wrong.

267
00:14:52,817 --> 00:14:54,386
What frustrates me is that...

268
00:14:55,886 --> 00:14:57,416
