00:32:49,905 --> 00:32:51,306
Please give me a chance.

537
00:32:56,915 --> 00:33:00,415
(Dowoon Physicist)

538
00:33:00,415 --> 00:33:03,026
(Dowoon Physicist)

539
00:33:03,026 --> 00:33:04,325
- Excuse me. - Yes?

540
00:33:04,325 --> 00:33:05,625
Do you have any inpatients?

541
00:33:06,026 --> 00:33:07,696
No. Is this your first visit?

542
00:33:09,496 --> 00:33:11,065
You really don't have any inpatients?

543
00:33:11,996 --> 00:33:14,365
We don't. What's ailing you?

544
00:33:14,365 --> 00:33:16,236
Can we look around the rooms?

545
00:33:16,966 --> 00:33:18,635
Hey, there's no one here.

546
00:33:18,966 --> 00:33:20,875
- We won't take long. - You can't go inside!

547
00:33:20,875 --> 00:33:22,075
Let us just check.

548
00:33:22,875 --> 00:33:24,645
- No! - Just this once.

549
00:33:24,645 --> 00:33:26,145
- You can't! - Just a look around.

550
00:33:47,896 --> 00:33:49,066
Mr. Bae!

551
00:33:51,606 --> 00:33:53,235
Leave us alone.

552
00:33:55,575 --> 00:33:56,746
Darn you.

553
00:34:03,646 --> 00:34:05,545
You brought a badly injured man to a physicist?

554
00:34:05,615 --> 00:34:07,086
Will you go away?

555
00:34:10,356 --> 00:34:11,485
Darn you!

556
00:34:13,856 --> 00:34:15,025
Wait!

557
00:34:16,295 --> 00:34:17,795
Why are you doing this?

558
00:34:17,896 --> 00:34:20,436
Han Soo. Byung Jin's alive.

559
00:34:20,496 --> 00:34:21,766
So just go away!

560
00:34:21,766 --> 00:34:23,306
Then nothing will happen!

561
00:34:23,306 --> 00:34:25,775
You neglected a severely injured man and tried to cover it up.

562
00:34:26,476 --> 00:34:28,005
If you don't stop,

563
00:34:28,005 --> 00:34:29,675
we'll all die here!

564
00:34:34,045 --> 00:34:35,985
She's my daughter. A beauty, right?

565
00:34:35,985 --> 00:34:38,016
She's the prettiest when she smiles.

566
00:34:49,695 --> 00:34:50,896
Mr. Bae.

567
00:34:50,896 --> 00:34:52,266
Calm down and look at me.

568
00:34:52,865 --> 00:34:54,595
Do you remember that time we talked in front of a bar?

569
00:34:54,896 --> 00:34:57,306
You boasted that your daughter has a beautiful smile.

570
00:34:57,666 --> 00:34:59,376
Your daughter is crying right now.

571
00:35:00,075 --> 00:35:01,306
Why is she crying?

572
00:35:01,436 --> 00:35:03,575
We visited her place to look for you.

573
00:35:03,646 --> 00:35:05,106
I explained to her what happened,

574
00:35:06,416 --> 00:35:07,445
and she cried.

575
00:35:12,516 --> 00:35:14,086
She says she's pregnant.

576
00:35:16,586 --> 00:35:18,726
You should live to see your grandchild.

577
00:35:40,746 --> 00:35:42,746
What a piece of junk.

578
00:36:25,825 --> 00:36:27,396
Hurry and get him out.

579
00:36:28,825 --> 00:36:29,896
Hey.

580
00:36:30,025 --> 00:36:31,865
Hey, get up.

581
00:37:06,735 --> 00:37:07,795
What is it?

582
00:37:07,936 --> 00:37:09,235
Mr. Seo,

583
00:37:09,235 --> 00:37:12,206
there was an accident.

584
00:37:12,206 --> 00:37:14,876
The tower crane toppled over.

585
00:37:15,336 --> 00:37:16,405
The operator...

586
00:37:17,175 --> 00:37:18,646
I think the operator died.

587
00:37:48,275 --> 00:37:50,106
Byung Jin? Byung Jin!

588
00:37:55,615 --> 00:37:57,985
(Dowoon Physicist)

589
00:37:59,586 --> 00:38:01,586
Are you crazy? Why would I get admitted to a hospital?

590
00:38:01,586 --> 00:38:03,255
You only work if you get paid under the table,

591
00:38:03,255 --> 00:38:05,255
so Byung Jin even switched turns...

592
00:38:05,255 --> 00:38:08,726
- and operated it in your place! - Then you should've paid me!

593
00:38:08,726 --> 00:38:10,226
- Darn it. - What?

594
00:38:12,936 --> 00:38:15,496
Do you need me to tell your wife that you're gambling again?

595
00:38:15,595 --> 00:38:17,706
Should I tell her you're throwing away half...

596
00:38:17,706 --> 00:38:18,766
of your wages gambling?

597
00:38:18,836 --> 00:38:20,505
- Gosh. - Hyung Il, please.

598
00:38:21,836 --> 00:38:23,445
It's just for a week.

599
00:38:23,445 --> 00:38:26,575
You'll get paid compensation too.

600
00:38:26,675 --> 00:38:29,316
I can't believe the things I do for you.

601
00:38:29,316 --> 00:38:31,316
- Gosh. Where to? - Thank you.

602
00:38:31,516 --> 00:38:33,086
Go.

603
00:38:43,295 --> 00:38:44,396
I'm sorry.

604
00:38:49,505 --> 00:38:50,936
Even if you were lucky,

605
00:38:51,666 --> 00:38:53,836
you should have a broken leg at least.

606
00:38:54,675 --> 00:38:55,836
Mr. Seo told me...

607
00:38:57,075 --> 00:38:59,845
the construction would be halted if anyone died.

608
00:39:01,345 --> 00:39:02,916
He said I'd be arrested.

609
00:39:02,916 --> 00:39:05,286
I was scared of that.

610
00:39:05,385 --> 00:39:08,416
But how did you dare do something so serious?

611
00:39:09,485 --> 00:39:11,686
I wanted to put up a nice wedding for my daughter,

612
00:39:14,095 --> 00:39:15,996
so I received money from Mr. Seo.

613
00:39:17,566 --> 00:39:19,536
Did you receive money from him?

614
00:39:20,836 --> 00:39:23,905
I knew the tower crane was faulty.

615
00:39:24,235 --> 00:39:27,235
He also promised the workers full-time jobs.

616
00:39:29,746 --> 00:39:31,345
Ever since I took that money,

617
00:39:31,905 --> 00:39:34,316
I became Mr. Seo's puppet.

618
00:39:39,016 --> 00:39:40,586
(Ward 2)

619
00:39:52,295 --> 00:39:53,695
Transfer him to the Naseon General Hospital.

620
00:40:04,075 --> 00:40:05,376
(Ambulance)

621
00:40:19,839 --> 00:40:20,527
(JU Construction)

622
00:40:20,676 --> 00:40:22,676
Something disgraceful happened at our company.

623
00:40:23,376 --> 00:40:24,906
Luckily, there were no deaths,

624
00:40:24,906 --> 00:40:27,276
so it won't make too much noise.

625
00:40:27,816 --> 00:40:29,745
The problem is with the testimony from the foreman.

626
00:40:30,716 --> 00:40:32,546
Apparently, he was ordered.

627
00:40:39,026 --> 00:40:42,225
When people are cornered, they're bound to make excuses.

628
00:40:42,865 --> 00:40:44,026
Is it irrelevant to you?

629
00:40:44,495 --> 00:40:47,665
What good would it do for me to order something like that?

630
00:40:47,796 --> 00:40:50,305
He hid someone nearing death to avoid trouble.

631
00:40:50,305 --> 00:40:51,606
Why would you listen to him?

632
00:40:52,535 --> 00:40:54,776
Let's treat some reporters to a meal and wrap it up.

633
00:40:55,975 --> 00:40:57,705
I heard the wall construction went well.

634
00:40:57,705 --> 00:41:00,115
We should go treat the workers to glasses of makgeolli.

635
00:41:00,645 --> 00:41:01,645
Let's do that.

636
00:41:02,446 --> 00:41:05,285
I request to perform a special audit on Mr. Seo Gil Pyo.

637
00:41:13,495 --> 00:41:15,156
I accuse him of these suspicions.

638
00:41:15,725 --> 00:41:16,765
"Suspicions?"

639
00:41:17,066 --> 00:41:18,696
How dare you?

640
00:41:19,495 --> 00:41:20,935
Our special audits include...

641
00:41:21,196 --> 00:41:25,265
Old Man Hwang and the major shareholders.

642
00:41:25,265 --> 00:41:26,336
(Proposal for Disciplinary Action)

643
00:41:26,336 --> 00:41:28,606
One slip and you could get humiliated,

644
00:41:29,176 --> 00:41:30,205
President Hwang.

645
00:41:36,046 --> 00:41:37,115
Please prepare it.

646
00:41:45,756 --> 00:41:46,856
That jerk...

647
00:41:58,865 --> 00:42:01,705
It's my fault. I was sloppy.

648
00:42:03,305 --> 00:42:04,376
Don't worry.

649
00:42:05,406 --> 00:42:08,415
You always cleaned up after me whenever I made a mess.

650
00:42:08,876 --> 00:42:10,645
You'd take Father's beating in my place too.

651
00:42:12,856 --> 00:42:15,816
This time, I'll repay you.

652
00:42:24,495 --> 00:42:27,566
Gosh, why didn't the foreman take the operator to the hospital?

653
00:42:27,736 --> 00:42:29,466
The punishment wouldn't have been much.

654
00:42:29,466 --> 00:42:32,606
Sometimes people make the wrong judgments.

655
00:42:32,606 --> 00:42:36,305
This is no time to sit back and relax.

656
00:42:36,305 --> 00:42:37,946
We're also guilty of taking bribes.

657
00:42:38,276 --> 00:42:39,845
What bribes?

658
00:42:40,946 --> 00:42:42,046
You're right.

659
00:42:42,046 --> 00:42:43,245
We did.

660
00:42:43,245 --> 00:42:44,745
Drinks, taxi fare, and gifts.

661
00:42:44,745 --> 00:42:47,055
It'd be a headache if all of these are taken into account.

662
00:42:47,455 --> 00:42:49,386
Gosh. Hey, Han Soo.

663
00:42:49,555 --> 00:42:50,886
Did Mr. Shin say anything about us?

664
00:42:50,886 --> 00:42:53,026
(Name: Hwang Dae Woong)

665
00:42:53,196 --> 00:42:54,926
I have to find the laptop.

666
00:42:54,926 --> 00:42:57,066
What are you saying? So did he or not?

667
00:42:59,865 --> 00:43:00,995
Hello.

668
00:43:00,995 --> 00:43:02,906
- Hello. - Hello.

669
00:43:03,106 --> 00:43:05,435
We'll perform a special audit on Mr. Seo Gil Pyo.

670
00:43:05,665 --> 00:43:08,035
It'll happen at 2pm on March 13 in the meeting room.

671
00:43:08,506 --> 00:43:11,546
The president, executives, staff, and major shareholders will attend.

672
00:43:12,406 --> 00:43:13,645
Please prepare for it thoroughly.

673
00:43:13,845 --> 00:43:15,075
- Okay. - Okay.

674
00:43:20,156 --> 00:43:21,486
Strange. How strange.

675
00:43:21,486 --> 00:43:23,356
He's performing a special audit on the senior managing director?

676
00:43:23,685 --> 00:43:26,325
He's wasting his time. He's digging his own grave.

677
00:43:26,325 --> 00:43:29,455
This will get Shin Cha Il fired for sure.

678
00:43:29,455 --> 00:43:31,665
Please, Mr. Yang.

679
00:43:32,466 --> 00:43:35,636
Luckily the laptop is gone. It would cause so much trouble.

680
00:43:35,895 --> 00:43:37,435
I'm amazed by the Vice President.

681
00:43:37,435 --> 00:43:38,665
I can't believe he burned it.

682
00:43:38,665 --> 00:43:40,636
Keep it down.

683
00:43:42,106 --> 00:43:43,406
Was the laptop burned?

684
00:43:44,075 --> 00:43:46,316
Did he really burn it?

685
00:43:47,316 --> 00:43:49,245
Have a good day, Mr. Yang.

686
00:43:49,845 --> 00:43:51,946
Mr. Gu, follow me. Come on.

687
00:43:52,645 --> 00:43:55,915
Han Soo. That's none of your business, isn't it?

688
00:43:55,915 --> 00:43:57,886
Your business is with Mr. Shin.

689
00:43:57,886 --> 00:44:01,026
Report his every move to us, Han Soo. Got it?

690
00:44:02,756 --> 00:44:05,995
I really regret listening to you.

691
00:44:07,595 --> 00:44:09,765
Good gracious. Hey.

692
00:44:20,245 --> 00:44:21,245
(Yeonseon Police Station)

693
00:44:21,245 --> 00:44:22,915
Allow me to visit him for a bit.

694
00:44:24,386 --> 00:44:25,415
Mr. Bae.

695
00:44:26,785 --> 00:44:28,386
What? Han Soo.

696
00:44:29,185 --> 00:44:30,225
What about Byung Jin?

697
00:44:31,926 --> 00:44:34,825
Mr. Ahn is a lot better now. And he'll get better.

698
00:44:36,526 --> 00:44:38,526
I shouldn't have followed the order.

699
00:44:39,196 --> 00:44:40,665
The moment I saw my daughter,

700
00:44:41,165 --> 00:44:42,865
I realized I committed a crime.

701
00:44:43,106 --> 00:44:46,066
Yes. It's a grave crime.

702
00:44:47,205 --> 00:44:50,305
You should get punished for your wrongdoings,

703
00:44:50,305 --> 00:44:51,946
but we should find out what you didn't do.

704
00:44:52,506 --> 00:44:55,316
On the day you talked with Mr. Seo over the phone.

705
00:44:56,075 --> 00:44:57,345
Did you record it?

706
00:44:57,645 --> 00:44:59,615
Of course not. I was all over the place.

707
00:45:15,765 --> 00:45:17,136
(Myung Tower President)

708
00:45:18,236 --> 00:45:19,535
Yes, Gu Han Soo speaking.

709
00:45:27,645 --> 00:45:31,046
The tower crane assembled with imported parts from overseas...

710
00:45:31,046 --> 00:45:33,256
- took the lives of workers... - Proper production standards...

711
00:45:33,256 --> 00:45:34,256
don't exist for tower cranes.

712
00:45:34,256 --> 00:45:35,986
Similar to traffic fatalities,

713
00:45:35,986 --> 00:45:38,126
- without circumlocution... - The tower crane accident...

714
00:45:38,126 --> 00:45:40,225
- was caused by old... - The tower crane that passed fit...

715
00:45:40,225 --> 00:45:41,955
- Had the accident... - The one...

716
00:45:41,955 --> 00:45:43,095
- not happened... - responsible...

717
00:45:57,475 --> 00:45:58,506
Mr. Shin.

718
00:46:02,546 --> 00:46:05,115
Myung Tower's President wants to continue our deal.

719
00:46:05,245 --> 00:46:07,316
He will testify during the special audit.

720
00:46:08,386 --> 00:46:11,486
Saying he can't hide the truth, he will disclose...

721
00:46:12,285 --> 00:46:14,356
the transfer details between him and Mr. Seo.

722
00:46:21,535 --> 00:46:23,265
I'm sorry I took the laptop.

723
00:46:33,006 --> 00:46:35,515
It was wrong of me, Mr. Shin.

724
00:46:50,225 --> 00:46:53,665
(JU Construction)

725
00:47:00,676 --> 00:47:02,106
It's been a while.

726
00:47:03,075 --> 00:47:04,075
Hi.

727
00:47:06,615 --> 00:47:09,716
Numerous special audits were held when your father was here.

728
00:47:09,716 --> 00:47:12,415
He loved it when people gathered.

729
00:47:12,546 --> 00:47:15,955
Shouldn't you mind your manners? He's the President now.

730
00:47:16,356 --> 00:47:19,426
Nonsense. I practically raised Se Woong.

731
00:47:26,466 --> 00:47:28,336
Don't cause any trouble.

732
00:47:28,736 --> 00:47:30,165
Keep this up, all right?

733
00:47:46,145 --> 00:47:47,415
You must be nervous.

734
00:47:50,656 --> 00:47:53,455
It's only natural. They'll give you the ax.

735
00:47:54,656 --> 00:47:58,196
And I really will chop your head off.

736
00:48:03,136 --> 00:48:05,066
No, stop it.

737
00:48:05,205 --> 00:48:07,975
Verbal abuse in companies is a big problem, right?

738
00:48:08,636 --> 00:48:11,676
Report me to the Ministry of Employment and Labor.

739
00:48:11,676 --> 00:48:12,805
I'll acknowledge what I did.

740
00:48:19,345 --> 00:48:23,386
(JU Construction)

741
00:48:32,495 --> 00:48:33,636
Where's Gu Han Soo?

742
00:48:33,736 --> 00:48:34,935
I'll give him a call.

743
00:48:36,236 --> 00:48:39,535
Thank you very much for making a tough decision, Mr. Park.

744
00:48:39,535 --> 00:48:41,776
Well, anyone would do the same.

745
00:48:43,475 --> 00:48:44,645
Here comes Mr. Shin.

746
00:49:08,796 --> 00:49:11,406
(JU Construction)

747
00:49:17,705 --> 00:49:19,475
I'm the Audit Team Manager Shin Cha Il.

748
00:49:20,145 --> 00:49:21,546
Let's start the special audit.

749
00:49:22,745 --> 00:49:25,446
Around 10am on January 16, 2024,

750
00:49:25,446 --> 00:49:27,386
a tower crane collapsed...

751
00:49:27,586 --> 00:49:30,185
at the construction site of Inpo Apartment.

752
00:49:30,856 --> 00:49:33,555
The missing certificate of manufacture...

753
00:49:33,555 --> 00:49:35,856
and the defect of the unapproved tower crane...

754
00:49:35,856 --> 00:49:37,196
were the cause of the accident.

755
00:49:37,696 --> 00:49:40,796
The Audit Team made an amateur mistake.

756
00:49:41,595 --> 00:49:43,836
Honorable President and executives.

757
00:49:44,165 --> 00:49:47,606
It is regrettable to hold such a meeting, regardless of all reasons.

758
00:49:48,406 --> 00:49:51,276
Our newly appointed Audit Team Manager...

759
00:49:51,606 --> 00:49:53,046
is too passionate.

760
00:49:55,645 --> 00:49:57,586
Historically speaking,

761
00:49:57,586 --> 00:49:59,515
as construction companies...

762
00:49:59,685 --> 00:50:02,156
could no longer possess tower cranes due to the IMF,

763
00:50:02,586 --> 00:50:05,256
they weren't obligated to submit certificates of manufacture.

764
00:50:05,526 --> 00:50:08,495
Hence, tower cranes weren't approved and wore out.

765
00:50:08,796 --> 00:50:10,796
That's why finding a decent tower crane...

766
00:50:11,165 --> 00:50:13,296
has become harder than finding a decent assemblyman.

767
00:50:13,895 --> 00:50:14,966
You are wrong.

768
00:50:15,136 --> 00:50:17,506
Certificate of manufacture has become mandatory years ago.

769
00:50:18,136 --> 00:50:20,136
We should've received a functional tower crane...

770
00:50:20,136 --> 00:50:22,305
with proper sorting and screening procedures.

771
00:50:22,305 --> 00:50:24,245
The construction cost us over 700 million dollars.

772
00:50:24,446 --> 00:50:27,075
Even a day of delay causes a big loss.

773
00:50:27,276 --> 00:50:29,376
We can't waste time on a tower crane.

774
00:50:29,376 --> 00:50:31,185
People's lives depend on it.

775
00:50:33,586 --> 00:50:36,185
You're determined to make me the bad guy, aren't you?

776
00:50:36,486 --> 00:50:39,656
Every year, 2,000 people die in car accidents.

777
00:50:39,825 --> 00:50:41,196
Even if sturdy cars...

778
00:50:41,196 --> 00:50:43,426
and safe roads are built,

779
00:50:43,626 --> 00:50:45,265
people die if luck is not on their side.

780
00:50:45,926 --> 00:50:48,535
The recent accident was purely out of bad luck.

781
00:50:48,535 --> 00:50:50,336
It is not such a wide-ranging issue.

782
00:50:50,336 --> 00:50:53,606
Less than ten tower cranes are used in an apartment construction site.

783
00:50:53,606 --> 00:50:55,606
Follow the rules strictly,

784
00:50:55,606 --> 00:50:57,176
and accidents can be prevented.

785
00:50:58,406 --> 00:51:00,115
You can't treat it with luck.

786
00:51:00,645 --> 00:51:02,716
I may look irresponsible,

787
00:51:02,816 --> 00:51:04,685
treating it with luck.

788
00:51:04,986 --> 00:51:06,756
But the result will be the same...

789
00:51:06,756 --> 00:51:08,515
regardless of who selects the tower cranes.

790
00:51:09,386 --> 00:51:12,426
Why did you pay for it as a functional tower crane?

791
00:51:12,886 --> 00:51:15,325
And why did you keep the difference...

792
00:51:15,555 --> 00:51:17,095
and not transfer it to the company?

793
00:51:18,696 --> 00:51:20,435
I kept the difference?

794
00:51:21,395 --> 00:51:22,736
Who said so?

795
00:51:22,736 --> 00:51:24,865
The President of Myung Tower, who supplies tower cranes...

796
00:51:24,865 --> 00:51:26,566
to JU Construction, will testify.

797
00:51:26,975 --> 00:51:28,035
What was that?

798
00:51:31,276 --> 00:51:34,345
Don't get nervous. Please only state the truth.

799
00:51:39,046 --> 00:51:40,356
How dare you slander me?

800
00:51:42,615 --> 00:51:45,725
Why would I slander you, Mr. Seo?

801
00:51:46,086 --> 00:51:47,156
I...

802
00:51:47,725 --> 00:51:50,926
