820
00:53:31,066 --> 00:53:33,066
- It's Foreman Bae. - Play this.

821
00:53:33,066 --> 00:53:35,265
Responsible for the site,

822
00:53:35,265 --> 00:53:37,506
Mr. Bae Young Sik knew the tower crane was defective.

823
00:53:38,136 --> 00:53:40,305
In order to stop him from talking,

824
00:53:40,506 --> 00:53:42,205
