867
00:55:27,415 --> 00:55:30,645
Criminal charges will be pressed by the police waiting outside.

868
00:55:31,745 --> 00:55:34,955
Myung Tower sells defective cranes and is a corrupt subcontractor.

869
00:55:34,955 --> 00:55:36,356
We must cut ties with them...

870
00:55:36,356 --> 00:55:37,955
and sue for damages.

871
00:55:41,325 --> 00:55:44,196
Yes. That is the right thing to do.

872
00:55:46,696 --> 00:55:49,265
I also demand Vice President Hwang be penalized.

873
00:55:51,435 --> 00:55:52,566
Vice President Hwang...

874
00:55:52,566 --> 00:55:55,836
damaged a laptop that held evidence in this investigation.

875
00:55:56,535 --> 00:55:57,946
You have two options.

876
00:55:57,946 --> 00:55:59,776
One, deny you didn't do so.

877
00:55:59,776 --> 00:56:01,876
Two, admit doing so and apologize.

878
00:56:02,716 --> 00:56:04,145
If you choose option one,

879
00:56:04,486 --> 00:56:07,156
I'll play CCTV footage of you burning the laptop.

880
00:56:08,685 --> 00:56:10,325
There were many cameras at the scene.

881
00:56:11,455 --> 00:56:12,586
The choice is yours.

882
00:56:37,415 --> 00:56:38,745
I apologize.

883
00:56:43,515 --> 00:56:46,656
JU Construction is working properly at last.

884
00:57:11,845 --> 00:57:13,446
Mr. Shin told me...

885
00:57:13,685 --> 00:57:15,015
to find the dashcam.

886
00:57:15,015 --> 00:57:17,955
He said Mr. Bae would know, so I visited him to ask.

887
00:57:18,256 --> 00:57:20,156
He said he'd smashed the dashcam...

888
00:57:20,156 --> 00:57:22,455
and dumped it in Mr. Choi's villa garbage site.

889
00:57:22,495 --> 00:57:23,595
So what?

890
00:57:23,966 --> 00:57:25,426
That was over a month ago.

891
00:57:26,026 --> 00:57:27,595
I searched all the garbage...

892
00:57:27,595 --> 00:57:29,365
wondering if it would be there.

893
00:57:29,435 --> 00:57:31,265
Dashcam memory cards are tiny.

894
00:57:31,265 --> 00:57:33,535
It was stuck in a corner of a garbage can...

895
00:57:33,535 --> 00:57:34,776
and I found it.

896
00:57:35,736 --> 00:57:37,205
Good for you, Gu Han Soo.

897
00:57:37,305 --> 00:57:38,876
- I'm impressed. - Thanks.

898
00:57:39,745 --> 00:57:40,745
Well done.

899
00:57:40,876 --> 00:57:42,276
What was Mr. Shin...

900
00:57:42,276 --> 00:57:45,415
going to do if you couldn't find the recording?

901
00:57:46,415 --> 00:57:47,656
- What do you think? - Goodness.

902
00:57:47,915 --> 00:57:48,955
Sorry.

903
00:57:48,955 --> 00:57:50,015
Why did you jump?

904
00:57:51,055 --> 00:57:53,026
I bet he'd have packed and run.

905
00:57:54,256 --> 00:57:55,555
Get back to work.

906
00:57:55,555 --> 00:57:58,495
Why make a fuss when you found just one thing?

907
00:57:58,495 --> 00:58:00,895
Goodness. You think you're amazing.

908
00:58:02,236 --> 00:58:04,265
