931
00:59:18,906 --> 00:59:20,276
He found the crane operator.

932
00:59:20,475 --> 00:59:23,345
If not, he could've died in that clinic.

933
00:59:23,716 --> 00:59:27,115
Our son knew the foreman wouldn't cross the line.

934
00:59:27,115 --> 00:59:28,955
He takes after me.

935
00:59:30,156 --> 00:59:31,185
